  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Hotelplan LTD (Inghams' parent company) strives to make ethical business choices when it comes to preventing modern slavery and human trafficking and will not knowingly support or deal with any business that engages in such practices. Furthermore, Hotelplan LTD confirms that it does not engage in modern slavery or human trafficking and that it takes reasonable steps with its supply chain to ensure it is not supporting modern slavery or human trafficking in any way.</p>
<p>This statement will be reviewed and published annually. This Statement is for the financial year ended <strong>31st October 2024.</strong></p>
<p>John Mansall - Inghams Managing Director </p>]]></bodyText>
